---
/**
 * Recognition / Credentials — the "title page" block
 * -------------------------------------------------------
 * A low-key, fact-forward section modelled on Osler's footer
 * ("50 practices ranked in Chambers Canada 2026") and on the
 * credentials strips run by Cravath, Sullivan & Cromwell, and
 * Davies. Copy is placeholder; numbers and logos are to be
 * finalised with the firm.
 */
---

<section class="relative bg-ink-950 text-paper-50">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px"
       style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--color-gold-600) 20%, var(--color-gold-500) 80%, transparent 100%);"
       aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-editorial py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-4">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-gold-400);">Credentials</span>
        <h2 class="mt-6 font-display font-semibold text-4xl leading-[1.05] text-paper-50 md:text-5xl">
          Documented, not claimed.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-sm text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-paper-200/70">
          Our authority rests on what has been filed in court, signed at
          closings, approved by regulators, and written into agreements —
          not on the adjectives a firm chooses for itself.
        </p>
      </div>

      <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:col-span-8 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Regulator</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-xl leading-tight text-paper-50">
            Member,<br />Law Society<br />of Ontario
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Structure</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-xl leading-tight text-paper-50">
            Limited<br />Liability<br />Partnership
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Partners</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-gold-400">
            04
          </dd>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xs text-paper-200/80">
            Three founding · one managing
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Offices</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-gold-400">
            03
          </dd>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xs text-paper-200/80">
            Toronto · Markham · Oakville
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Practice Areas</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-gold-400">
            08
          </dd>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xs text-paper-200/80">
            Disclosed scope; we refer out where we should.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Languages</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-xl leading-tight text-paper-50">
            English<br />
            Mandarin · Cantonese<br />
            Punjabi · Hindi
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Admissions</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-xl leading-tight text-paper-50">
            Superior Court<br />
            Court of Appeal<br />
            for Ontario
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-ink-800 pt-5">
          <dt class="smallcaps text-[10.5px] text-gold-400">Established</dt>
          <dd class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-none text-gold-400">
            2024
          </dd>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xs text-paper-200/80">
            Founded in Toronto, Ontario
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <!-- Small caveat / attorney advertising disclaimer — institutional signal -->
    <p class="mt-14 max-w-3xl text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-paper-200/35">
      Attorney Advertising · The material on this website is provided for
      general information only and is not legal advice.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
